What is your overall assessment of this course?
Do you expect to use this class for credit toward your major, or toward a pre-professional program?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I think the two semester option is a lot better than the one semester option.
The yearlong project is a pain, but I honestly couldn't imagine completing the process in one semester.

Year-long senior project. Very flexible, pretty fun to get involved into a project and delve deeply into it for an entire year. I would recommend the two-semester rather than the one-semester, as its not that much more work and much more rewarding.
